data.description: Welcome to you home away from home in the beautiful Arrowhead Lake Community.  This stylish contemporary mountain retreat offers 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The large windows and slider doors allow for plenty of light while enjoying the warm of the stone fireplace.  The open floor plan is prefect for entertaining family and friend while still being able to prepare your meals.  With the warm weather coming you can also spend time entertaining on the spacious deck while enjoying the serenity of your private surroundings.  Schedule your appointment today.  This home is being sold fully furnished.  The seller has recently made exterior repairs to the home and it motivated to sell.
